---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { url } from '@lib/url';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About + Editorial Standards - GeorgiaBooked"
  description="Our mission, methodology, and editorial standards for publishing Georgia public arrest records."
>
  <article class="max-w-narrow mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="mb-10">
      <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-7xl font-semibold mt-4 mb-5 text-balance" style="letter-spacing: -0.035em; line-height: 0.95; font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 72;">
        Public records, <span class="italic text-crimson" style="font-style: italic;">plainly published</span>.
      </h1>
      <p class="display-dek text-textSecondary text-xl md:text-2xl max-w-2xl text-pretty">
        An independent, journalist-run public-records publication for the state of Georgia.
      </p>
    </div>

    <hr class="rule-hair my-10" />

    <section class="mb-10">
      <span class="eyebrow-muted">Our mission</span>
      <p class="font-serif text-xl md:text-2xl leading-relaxed text-textPrimary mt-4 drop-cap text-pretty" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 24;">
        Georgia's Open Records Act (Ga. Code 50-18-72) makes arrest and booking records public because transparent accountability of the criminal justice system is a cornerstone of a functioning democracy. GeorgiaBooked publishes those records in a searchable, verifiable, and navigable format, so that Georgians can follow what is happening in their own counties.
      </p>
    </section>

    <hr class="rule-hair my-10" />

    <section class="mb-10">
      <span class="eyebrow-muted">Editorial standards</span>
      <ul class="mt-6 space-y-5">
        <li class="hairline-top pt-5">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-textPrimary mb-1.5" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">Factual only.</h3>
          <p class="text-textSecondary leading-relaxed">Each entry reflects public records from county sheriff offices or verified aggregators. No speculation, no editorial commentary on guilt or character.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="hairline-top pt-5">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-textPrimary mb-1.5" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">Presumption of innocence.</h3>
          <p class="text-textSecondary leading-relaxed">Every arrest page carries a visible disclaimer. An arrest is an allegation, not a conviction.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="hairline-top pt-5">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-textPrimary mb-1.5" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">Prompt corrections.</h3>
          <p class="text-textSecondary leading-relaxed">Factual errors are corrected within 72 hours. Expunged or dismissed records are removed on verification.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="hairline-top pt-5">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-textPrimary mb-1.5" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">No pay-to-remove.</h3>
          <p class="text-textSecondary leading-relaxed">We do not accept payment to remove records. Takedowns are free and reviewed on the merits.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <hr class="rule-hair my-10" />

    <section class="mb-10">
      <span class="eyebrow-muted">Methodology</span>
      <p class="text-textPrimary leading-relaxed mt-4 text-lg">
        Booking data is aggregated hourly from public Georgia sources. Each entry is summarized into neutral, factual prose using a large language model (Gemini 2.5), then programmatically classified by charge severity. Mugshot photos are sourced from original publishers.
      </p>
    </section>

    <hr class="rule-hair my-10" />

    <section>
      <span class="eyebrow-muted">Contact</span>
      <p class="text-textPrimary leading-relaxed mt-4 text-lg">
        For factual corrections or takedowns: <a href={url('/takedown')} class="text-crimson hover:underline">takedown form</a>.<br/>
        For press, partnership, or advertising inquiries: <span class="font-mono tabular text-gold">press@georgiabooked.com</span>
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
